    {
      "id": "pwu_why",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "structure": "30",
        "background_background": "classic",
        "background_color": "#fdf6ef",
        "padding": {"unit":"px","top":"80","right":"32","bottom":"80","left":"32","isLinked":false},
        "content_width": {"unit":"px","size":1320}
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "pwu_why_col_intro",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {"_column_size": 100},
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "pwu_why_h",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "WHY PARTNER <span style='color:#ff6e6e'>WITH US?</span>",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center",
                "title_color": "#6a1753",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Cormorant Garamond",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit":"px","size":48},
                "typography_font_weight": "400",
                "typography_letter_spacing": {"unit":"px","size":-1},
                "typography_text_transform": "uppercase"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "pwu_why_sub",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='text-align:center;max-width:880px;margin:16px auto 48px;'>CIWA offers diverse partnership opportunities tailored to your organization's goals and values. Discover how you can make a meaningful impact.</p>",
                "text_color": "#4a4a4a",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Inter",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit":"px","size":17},
                "typography_line_height": {"unit":"em","size":1.55}
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "pwu_why_cards_html",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<style>.pwu-why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:32px;max-width:1320px;margin:0 auto}.pwu-why-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #ece2eb;border-radius:14px;padding:36px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)}.pwu-why-card img{width:48px;height:48px;display:block}.pwu-why-card h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:400;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.4px}.pwu-why-card.purple h3{color:#6a1753}.pwu-why-card.orange h3{color:#f68b3c}.pwu-why-card.pink h3{color:#e22371}.pwu-why-card p{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a4a4a;margin:0}@media(max-width:900px){.pwu-why-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style><div class='pwu-why-grid'><div class='pwu-why-card purple'><img src='{ASSETS}/programs/icon-1.svg' alt=''><h3>Support Thousands</h3><p>You actively support thousands of immigrant women in building successful lives and contribute to community wellbeing.</p></div><div class='pwu-why-card orange'><img src='{ASSETS}/programs/icon-2.svg' alt=''><h3>Diversity &amp; Inclusion</h3><p>You demonstrate your organization's commitment to diversity and inclusion while addressing critical workforce gaps.</p></div><div class='pwu-why-card pink'><img src='{ASSETS}/programs/icon-3.svg' alt=''><h3>Skilled Professionals</h3><p>You gain access to a wide pool of skilled professionals ready to contribute meaningfully to your business.</p></div></div>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pwu_tabs",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "background_background": "classic",
        "background_color": "#ffffff",
        "padding": {"unit":"px","top":"64","right":"32","bottom":"96","left":"32","isLinked":false},
        "content_width": {"unit":"px","size":1320}
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "pwu_tabs_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {"_column_size": 100},
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "pwu_tabs_html",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<style>.pwu-tabs-nav{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #d6c8d4;display:flex;gap:0}.pwu-tab{padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px;color:#8a7a87;text-transform:uppercase;text-align:center;flex:1}.pwu-tab.active{color:#6a1753;border-bottom-color:#6a1753}.pwu-intro{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto 48px;text-align:center;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a4a4a}.pwu-cards-2x2{max-width:1320px;margin:0 auto 56px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px}.pwu-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6dce4;border-left:6px solid #6a1753;border-radius:14px;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}.pwu-card.purple{border-left-color:#6a1753}.pwu-card.purple h3{color:#6a1753}.pwu-card.pink{border-left-color:#e22371}.pwu-card.pink h3{color:#e22371}.pwu-card.orange{border-left-color:#f68b3c}.pwu-card.orange h3{color:#f68b3c}.pwu-card h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:400;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.4px}.pwu-card p{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a4a4a;margin:0}.pwu-work{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6dce4;border-left:6px solid #5bbdad;border-radius:14px;padding:36px;margin:0 auto 56px;max-width:1320px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}.pwu-work h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:400;margin:0 0 14px;color:#5bbdad;text-transform:uppercase}.pwu-work p{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a4a4a;margin:0 0 20px}.pwu-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}.pwu-tag{background:#eaf6f3;color:#2d6f64;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}.pwu-twoup{max-width:1320px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px}@media(max-width:900px){.pwu-cards-2x2,.pwu-twoup{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style><div class='pwu-tabs-nav'><div class='pwu-tab active'>FOR BUSINESS</div><div class='pwu-tab'>FOR COMMUNITY PARTNERS</div></div><p class='pwu-intro'>CIWA works with over 150 business partners each and every year, making a significant impact by volunteering time, knowledge, space, or offering employment to newcomers in Calgary.</p><div class='pwu-cards-2x2'><div class='pwu-card purple'><h3>Networking with Newcomers</h3><p>Participate in networking events to meet immigrant women entering the Canadian workforce.</p><p>Help newcomers navigate resumes, interviews, and job applications.</p></div><div class='pwu-card pink'><h3>Host a Work Placement or Practicum</h3><p>Provide work placements for immigrant women enrolled in CIWA programs.</p><p>Offer practical Canadian work experience, helping participants overcome employment barriers.</p></div><div class='pwu-card purple'><h3>Hire Graduates</h3><p>Employ qualified CIWA alumnae trained in childcare, customer service, office administration, and more.</p><p>Support economic security for immigrant women and their families.</p></div><div class='pwu-card pink'><h3>Refer Job Seekers</h3><p>Direct immigrant women not yet job-ready to CIWA's bridge-to-work programs.</p><p>Free training in retail, food service, security, hospitality, and interpretation.</p></div></div><div class='pwu-work'><h3>Host a Work Experience</h3><p>CIWA works with employers to host work placements for employment-ready immigrant women. Employers benefit from a motivated workforce, while participants gain practical Canadian work experience that opens doors to long-term careers.</p><div class='pwu-tags'><span class='pwu-tag'>Accounting</span><span class='pwu-tag'>Office administration</span><span class='pwu-tag'>Management</span><span class='pwu-tag'>Sales and Marketing</span><span class='pwu-tag'>IT</span><span class='pwu-tag'>Childcare</span><span class='pwu-tag'>Retail</span></div></div><div class='pwu-twoup'><div class='pwu-card orange'><h3>Be a Corporate or Community Sponsor</h3><p>Amplify CIWA's impact by sponsoring initiatives that break barriers for immigrant women.</p><p>Host space for events or provide in-kind services to support programs.</p></div><div class='pwu-card purple'><h3>Access Diverse Talent</h3><p>Join CIWA's free platform for employers, \"Diverse Workforce,\" to connect with qualified immigrant women across sectors.</p></div></div>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
